All snack board enthusiasts know: a balance of sweet and savory is key! We whipped up a seasonal snack board with @cafigs and Feedfeed’s @clarelangan. 
👉 Did you know California Fresh Fig season is now thru November? When you see them, buy them! Find @cafigs near you by visiting your local grocery retailer. 
👉 Want more fig inspo? Check out our Fig Feed! https://thefeedfeed.com/figs and follow @cafigs #feedfeed #figs

node.text:
Use @filippoberio_us for all of your baking needs (#ad)! Heart-healthy #FilippoBerio Olive Oil takes butter’s place, which is what’s traditionally used in pie dough, for these Balsamic, Blackberry, and Ricotta Hand Pies. The olive oil sub along with the use of #vegan ricotta cheese makes this a #dairyfree treat! The recipe makes 8 of the cutest personal pies, perfect for summer picnics and days outdoors.

👉Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/fb-handpies #feedfeed #oliveoil #hearthealthy #pie #feedfeed #blackberry #baking #smallbatch

node.text: Editorial director @clarelangan sat down with Julia to talk about what Pride means to her and her tips for summer cooking! Check out her new book Simply Julia and her recipe for her Ricotta and Potato Chip Fish Cakes via the link in our bio!

node.title: Celebrate Pride month with cookbook author Julia Turshen @turshen

node.text:
You haven't tasted cinnamon until you've tried Single Origin by @SimplyOrganicFoods Vietnamese Cinnamon (#ad). It has a strong, sweet, and rich flavor that works well in everything from cocktails to savory applications. This Cinnamon Scented Iced Coffee is inspired by traditional Vietnamese coffee and it is sure to become a favorite for a morning or afternoon pick-me-up!
👆Get the recipe by clicking the link in our bio or by visiting ff.recipes/cinn-vietnamese-coffee
👉To learn more about @SimplyOrganicFoods and their new Single Origin Line, visit ff.recipes/so-singleorigin
Recipe by Team Feedfeed's Senior Food Editor @mollyjeanadams 
🎥 & 📷 by Team Feedfeed's @hungryforhistory and @lmsthompson 
#feedfeed #simplyorganic #simplyorganicfoods #cinnamon #caffiene #coffee #icedcoffee #coffeelover
